The fibroblast involved in scarring and contraction is the [[myofibroblast]],<ref name=myo201103/> which is a specialized contractile fibroblast.<ref name=myo2011033/> These cells express a-smooth muscle actin (a-SMA).<ref name=myosm201103>{{Cite web
